  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PeakPals</strong> is a vertical climbing game where your goal is simple: <strong>reach the airship waiting at the very top</strong>.<br>But with 2500 meters of platforms, one mistake can send you all the way back down.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🗻 Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A massive 2500-meter level</strong> – every meter counts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Different platform types</strong> – including sound-cued falling platforms that keep you on edge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achievements</strong> – progress milestones across Easy, Medium & Hard difficulties</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Checkpoint system</strong> – Easy mode gives you a checkpoint every ~100m, Medium every ~500m</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hard mode</strong> – zero checkpoints, pure skill and endurance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer (1–6 players) – climb together or race to the top with friends</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 Game Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beginner (Easy)</strong> – forgiving, frequent checkpoints</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Medium</strong> – balanced challenge with fewer checkpoints</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hard</strong> – no checkpoints at all. Only the best will survive.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Do you have the patience, precision, and nerves of steel to conquer 2500 meters of chaos – alone or together with friends in 1–6 player multiplayer?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every fall will test your willpower, every jump brings you closer to glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Laugh, rage, repeat… until you finally reach the airship at the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960540/extras/455f402b683dbf7e7adcf21ea8b28786.poster.avif?t=1760343195\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960540/extras/455f402b683dbf7e7adcf21ea8b28786.webm?t=1760343195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960540/extras/455f402b683dbf7e7adcf21ea8b28786.mp4?t=1760343195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
